<div class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-100 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
        <div class="bg-purple-600 rounded-full p-3 shadow-lg">
          <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12a2 2 0 004 0m0 0a2 2 0 104 0 4 4 0 11-8 0zm5 5v1a3 3 0 01-6 0v-1m6 0V9a3 3 0 00-6 0v7.5m6-7.5h.5a2 2 0 11-3 0h2.5z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">경매용 차량 등록</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600">경매에 올릴 차량을 등록합니다 (관리자 승인 후 경매 개설 가능)</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8">

      <%= form_with(model: @vehicle, local: true, multipart: true, html: { class: "space-y-6" }) do |form| %>
        <% if @vehicle.errors.any? %>
          <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
            <div class="flex">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-red-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.707 7.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L8.586 10l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 11.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L11.414 10l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 8.586 8.707 7.293z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-3">
                <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-red-800">
                  <%= pluralize(@vehicle.errors.count, "개의 오류") %>가 발생했습니다
                </h3>
                <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-red-700">
                  <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
                    <% @vehicle.errors.full_messages.each do |message| %>
                      <li><%= message %></li>
                    <% end %>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <!-- 차량 기본 정보 -->
          <div class="md:col-span-2">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">차량 정보</h3>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <%= form.label :title, "차량명", class: "block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2" %>
            <%= form.text_field :title,
                class: "appearance-none block w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg shadow-sm placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-purple-500 transition-colors",
                placeholder: "예: 2020년 현대 아반떼 1.6 가솔린" %>
          </div>

          <div>
            <%= form.label :brand, "브랜드", class: "block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2" %>
            <%= form.select :brand, 
                options_for_select([
                  ['현대', '현대'],
                  ['기아', '기아'],
                  ['삼성', '삼성'],
                  ['쌍용', '쌍용'],
                  ['르노삼성', '르노삼성'],
                  ['BMW', 'BMW'],
                  ['벤츠', '벤츠'],
                  ['아우디', '아우디'],
                  ['폭스바겐', '폭스바겐'],
                  ['미니', '미니'],
                  ['토요타', '토요타'],
                  ['혼다', '혼다'],
                  ['닛산', '닛산'],
                  ['인피니티', '인피니티'],
                  ['렉서스', '렉서스'],
                  ['마쯔다', '마쯔다'],
                  ['스바루', '스바루'],
                  ['포드', '포드'],
                  ['쉐보레', '쉐보레'],
                  ['지프', '지프'],
                  ['테슬라', '테슬라'],
                  ['볼보', '볼보'],
                  ['재규어', '재규어'],
                  ['랜드로버', '랜드로버'],
                  ['포르쉐', '포르쉐'],
                  ['페라리', '페라리'],
                  ['람보르기니', '람보르기니'],
                  ['벤틀리', '벤틀리'],
                  ['롤스로이스', '롤스로이스'],
                  ['맥라렌', '맥라렌'],
                  ['기타', '기타']
                ], @vehicle.brand),
                { prompt: '브랜드를 선택하세요' },
                { class: "appearance-none block w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg shadow-sm bg-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-purple-500 transition-colors" } %>
          </div>

          <div>
            <%= form.label :model, "모델", class: "block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2" %>
            <%= form.text_field :model,
                class: "appearance-none block w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg shadow-sm placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-purple-500 transition-colors",
                placeholder: "아반떼" %>
          </div>

          <div>
            <%= form.label :year, "연식", class: "block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2" %>
            <%= form.number_field :year,
                class: "appearance-none block w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg shadow-sm placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-purple-500 transition-colors",
                placeholder: "2020",
                min: 1990,
                max: Date.current.year + 1 %>
          </div>

          <div>
            <%= form.label :mileage, "주행거리 (km)", class: "block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2" %>
            <%= form.number_field :mileage,
                class: "appearance-none block w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg shadow-sm placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-purple-500 transition-colors",
                placeholder: "50000",
                min: 0 %>
          </div>

          <div>
            <%= form.label :fuel_type, "연료 타입", class: "block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2" %>
            <%= form.select :fuel_type,
                options_for_select([
                  ['가솔린', 'gasoline'],
                  ['디젤', 'diesel'],
                  ['하이브리드', 'hybrid'],
                  ['전기', 'electric'],
                  ['LPG', 'lpg'],
                  ['수소', 'hydrogen'],
                  ['CNG', 'cng'],
                  ['기타', 'other']
                ], @vehicle.fuel_type),
                { prompt: '연료 타입을 선택하세요' },
                { class: "appearance-none block w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg shadow-sm bg-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-purple-500 transition-colors" } %>
          </div>

          <div>
            <%= form.label :transmission, "변속기", class: "block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2" %>
            <%= form.select :transmission,
                options_for_select([
                  ['자동', 'automatic'],
                  ['수동', 'manual'],
                  ['CVT', 'cvt']
                ], @vehicle.transmission),
                { prompt: '변속기를 선택하세요' },
                { class: "appearance-none block w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg shadow-sm bg-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-purple-500 transition-colors" } %>
          </div>

          <div class="md:col-span-2">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 mt-6">경매 정보</h3>
          </div>

          <div>
            <%= form.label :starting_price, "시작가 (원)", class: "block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2" %>
            <%= form.number_field :starting_price, 
                class: "appearance-none block w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg shadow-sm placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-purple-500 transition-colors",
                placeholder: "1000000",
                min: 0,
                step: 10000 %>
          </div>

          <div>
            <%= form.label :reserve_price, "희망가 (원)", class: "block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2" %>
            <%= form.number_field :reserve_price, 
                class: "appearance-none block w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg shadow-sm placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-purple-500 transition-colors",
                placeholder: "25000000",
                min: 0,
                step: 10000 %>
          </div>

          <!-- 상세 설명 -->
          <div class="md:col-span-2">
            <%= form.label :description, "상세 설명", class: "block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2" %>
            <%= form.text_area :description, rows: 6,
                class: "appearance-none block w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg shadow-sm placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-purple-500 transition-colors resize-none",
                placeholder: "차량 상태, 특이사항, 옵션 등을 자세히 설명해주세요..." %>
          </div>

          <!-- 차량 사진 -->
          <div class="md:col-span-2">
            <%= form.label :images, "차량 사진", class: "block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2" %>
            <%= form.file_field :images, multiple: true, accept: "image/*",
                class: "appearance-none block w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg shadow-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-purple-500 transition-colors" %>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">여러 장의 사진을 업로드할 수 있습니다. (JPG, PNG 권장)</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 안내사항 -->
        <div class="bg-purple-50 border border-purple-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-purple-800 mb-4">경매 등록 안내사항</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-purple-700">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-purple-500 mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              차량 등록 후 관리자 승인을 거쳐 경매가 시작됩니다
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-purple-500 mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              정확한 차량 정보와 상태를 기재해주세요
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-purple-500 mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              선명한 차량 사진을 여러 장 업로드하시면 입찰률이 높아집니다
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-purple-500 mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              경매 낙찰 시 플랫폼 수수료가 적용됩니다
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- 제출 버튼 -->
        <div class="flex justify-end space-x-4 pt-6">
          <%= link_to "취소", vehicles_path, 
              class: "px-6 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg text-gray-700 font-medium hover:bg-gray-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-purple-500 transition-colors" %>
          <%= form.submit "차량 등록",
              class: "px-8 py-3 bg-purple-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-purple-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-purple-500 transition-colors duration-200 shadow-lg border border-purple-600" %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
